After install, type in the Firefox location

about:config

Press right mouse button, select New->String

Enter name: network.mstream.path

Enter value: path to the media streamer

VLC or mplayer or other, for example c:\program files\videolan\vlc\vlc.exe

After that all links started with mstream:// will be passed directly to vlc 
or mplayer for streaming play.

Examples:

mstream://localhost/movies/TheMask.avi

